  <h2>谁读这本书?</h2>
  <div class="indent" id="collector">

    

<div class="">
    
    <div class="ll"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/xyws/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1040411-2.jpg" class="pil" alt="逍遥未遂" /></a></div>
    <div style="padding-left:60px"><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/people/xyws/">逍遥未遂</a><br/>
      <div class="pl ll">          44分钟前          读过      </div>

        <span class="allstar30" title="还行"></span>
      <br/>

      <span class="pl">tags:小说</span><br />

          <span class="">意义观不是与生俱来一成不变的本能，恰恰相反，它们只是一时的时尚、习惯以及文化倾向</span> <br/>
    </div>
    <div class="clear"></div><br/>
    <div class="ul" style="margin-bottom:12px;"></div>
